subsection.content:
tracing, restraining, forfeiting and confiscating
                    property used in or derived from criminal activities and the proceeds of
                    criminal activities;

the request for assistance impairs the sovereignty,
                    security or public order of Australia or, in the case of Hong Kong, of the State
                    which is responsible for the foreign affairs relating to Hong Kong;

a description of the nature of the investigation,
                    prosecution, offence or criminal matter and whether or not proceedings have been
                    instituted;

the court order, if any, or a certified copy
                    thereof, sought to be enforced and a statement to the effect that it is a final
                    order;
